name: paraviewweb
description: Web framework for building interactive visualization relying on VTK or ParaView to produce visualization data

packageJSON.name: paraviewweb
packageJSON.description: Web framework for building interactive visualization relying on VTK or ParaView to produce visualization data

scripts.build:release: npm run bin:fix-autobahn && export NODE_ENV=production && npm run build -- -p
scripts.semantic-release: semantic-release pre && npm publish && semantic-release post

commit.message:
feat(ParaViewWeb): Initial codebase for the ParaViewWeb framework/library

ParaViewWeb aims to provide a set of tools for doing Scientific Visualization in the Web while
relying on VTK or ParaView to process heavy data and eventually generate new dataset meant for your
browser.
